        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"149780\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"149780\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>You and me both. Did you taste the 2008 Bienvenues-B\u00e2tard? It\u2019s high up my wish list.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>No 08 BBM. I\u2019ve had the 09, which turned me on to Louis C\u202604 with its ripping acidity and a little more ox showing than a couple 01\u2019s which were flat out amazing\u2026and an old dude 84 that was plenty alive, soft and quite elegant. Love how pure and alive his wines are!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p><img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/9/99a8907a1d5b3c023582052741dc72dc9823c044.gif\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" alt=\"[worship.gif]\" title=\"worship\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n<p>Awesome wines\u2026</p>",
